      "name": "Osint_confidence",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/confidence",
      "description": "The confidence of an indicator being malicious and/or pertinent, normalized to\nthe caption of the confidence_id value. In the case of 'Other', it is defined\nby the event source or analyst.",
