          "annotations": {}
        }
      },
      "description": "<p>The normalized identifier of the event/finding severity.</p>The normalized\nseverity is a measurement the effort and expense required to manage and resolve\nan event or incident. Smaller numerical values represent lower impact events,\nand larger numerical values represent higher impact events.",
