      "description": "This attribute relates a sub-script to a parent script having the matching\n<code>uid</code> attribute. In the case of PowerShell, sub-script execution can\nbe identified by matching the activity correlation ID of the raw ETW events\nprovided by the OS.",
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/dictionary",
      "aliases": [
