      "description": "The original event time as reported by the event source. For example, the time\nin the original format from system event log such as Syslog on Unix/Linux and\nthe System event file on Windows. Omit if event is generated instead of\ncollected via logs.",
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/dictionary",
