      "description": "The Operating System (OS) object describes characteristics of an OS, such as\nLinux or Windows.",
      "notes": [
        "D3FEND\u2122 Ontology d3f:OperatingSystem \u2014\nhttps://d3fend.mitre.org/dao/artifact/d3f:OperatingSystem/"
      ],
