      "name": "CisCsc",
      "definition_uri": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/CisCsc",
      "description": "The CIS Critical Security Control (CSC) contains information as defined by the\nCenter for Internet Security Critical Security Control <a target='_blank'\nhref='https://www.cisecurity.org/controls'>(CIS CSC)</a>. Prioritized set of\nactions to protect your organization and data from cyber-attack vectors.",
      "deprecated": "Use the cis_control object instead. (since 1.5.0)",
