          "tag": "observable_id",
          "value": 30,
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "The Fingerprint object provides detailed information about a fingerprint, which\nis a compact representation of data used to identify a longer piece of\ninformation, such as a public key, file content, or application implementation.\nIt contains the algorithm or scheme and value of the fingerprint, enabling\nefficient and reliable identification of the associated data.",
      "notes": [
        "D3FEND\u2122 Ontology d3f:DigitalFingerprint. \u2014\nhttps://d3fend.mitre.org/dao/artifact/d3f:DigitalFingerprint/"
      ],
      "in_subset": [
        "objects_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/objects",
