          "tag": "ocsf_profile",
          "value": "osint",
          "@type": "Annotation"
        }
      ],
      "description": "The OSINT (Open Source Intelligence) profile contains one or more indicators\nand associated analysis and details, such as registrar (WHOIS) information and\ncommentary about a hostname, or information about a digital certificate and its\nusage within a campaign. This information can be used to further enrich a\ndetection or finding by providing decisioning support to other analysts and\nengineers within the profile itself.",
      "in_subset": [
        "osint_profile_subset"
      ],
      "from_schema": "https://w3id.org/lmodel/ocsf/profiles",
